giant dormant robot? Oh well that changes everything I mean I myself have the 
controller for it. Its a special button with the windows sign. And yes there 
is arule against declaring the moon as a giant robot you want to use against 
the base. Its called stating it without asking the council about it since 
there is a rule about bringing in Battlecruisers(Which are a helluva lot 
smaller then the moon) and asking the council about bringing it in.
